{"tid":1396781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲記唔記得 SAYA Chan ?","createTime":"2019-08-02T08:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T06:37:56.000Z","uid":118346,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b708a27440924a59b04626245d2546bf16247442","tid":1396781,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E5%B9%B8%E7%81%BD%E6%A8%82%E7%A6%8D%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B7%259D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E7%2581%25BD%25E6%25A8%2582%25E7%25A6%258D%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=dea94a90\" target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E5%B9%B8%E7%81%BD%E6%A8%82%E7%A6%8D%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a>"},{"pid":"fe307234a92552dc51ad42f5b805c8736e3ac34c","tid":1396781,"uid":118346,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"5.12四川大地震成為全城熱話<br />\n世界各地已經捐左 n咁多錢唻幫四川既&quot;人&quot;<br />\n點解無人肯捐比四川既熊貓??<br />\n5.16學校早會搞左個四川唔知咩<br />\n放左 d片有段 d人係咁喊<br />\n佢地喊到好似笑咁搞到我笑左幾野<br />\n我對四川真係可以講係無感情<br />\n關我叉事咩??<br />\n我睇 d新聞仲可以笑得出<br />\n完全無覺得傷心同情之類<br />\n何必搞到自己唔開心呢??<br />\n咁打後果一星期真係要喊哂口??<br />\n已經捐左咁多錢仲要我捐??你無野阿??=]<br />\n自己都唔夠用仲要比人用?都痴痴地既 XD<br />\n原來見其他人都捐自己都唔捐係咁爽 XD<br />\n個個都捐多我一個唔多少我一個唔少啦<br />\n唔捐都有3萬6千以上<br />\n四川都發達 tim啦<br />\n外國仲要用美元歐元英鎊<br />\n?過唻人民幣咩都夠啦係咪阿??<br />\n大陸 d野仲要咁平..<br />\n咩都夠 Q哂啦<br />\n你地係咪嫌錢多先??係既唔該比熊貓<br />\n熊貓係中國獨有動物已列入世界級保護動物<br />\n四川已經係死城真係 o徙錢<br />\n呢家 d野咩都加價留返 d錢比自己好無??<br />\n死多 d咪好￼醫院唔洗咁迫<br />\n唔洗無位唔洗怕無得安置佢地<br />\n唔怕唔夠物資唔洗怕人口過多<br />\n少左 d人排放所有垃圾<br />\n死多個人又有大把人捐錢<br />\n你地話係咪死好過唔死先 XD<br />\n還掂都死左咁多件唔差左死多5千個=]<br />\n鬼叫佢地大陸咁鐘意貪污<br />\n佢地死做乜要連累我地喎??<br />\n個個機構學校乜叉乜叉都搞捐款<br />\n我地 d錢仲得了既??<br />\n我地 d錢唔係要比 d死屍用嫁<br />\n唔該有 d貢獻好無阿??<br />\n唔好咁盲目啦佢地咁可憐<br />\n咁鐘意捐捐哂你地副身家阿笨<br />\n人地其實國家捐千萬<br />\n你地捐得果10$以上幫到 d乜叉阿??<br />\nPS請勿再傻請勿再捐無謂既錢<br />\n<br />\n原來當年 MK 妹行先我地10年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f99e60f8eccc78d68484e80c67d2df74ff7489","tid":1396781,"uid":17154,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"其實某啲點佢真係幾有道理，關我地撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911752b0ba84e1ca7e438f38f8aa22450edc3cd8","tid":1396781,"uid":237425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"警世鴻文<br />\n<br />\n下次支那又要叫人籌錢又要POST"},{"pid":"2a04ce3b0e1afa3e9986865bc152b23c287492fd","tid":1396781,"uid":50658,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:14:52.000Z","msg":"走得太前<br />\n同陳巧文一樣"},{"pid":"c25a159e062947f1b1924a01bd813bebf464bdf7","tid":1396781,"uid":52349,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"08年高登<br />\n大家心照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5381c894c120f26e1bf9ec8241e801747baee6","tid":1396781,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:16:09.000Z","msg":"行得太前 快過我地十幾年  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4236dcf832e4ec57d871d1ef1687600b1b6c8acc","tid":1396781,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"當年個個都大中華膠<br />\n又愛國不愛黨<br />\nd人唔屌鳩佢就奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk